## <a id="personal-details"></a>Personal Use License

The Personal Use License is free and grants you the right to use poko capsule website for non-commercial purposes.

### Who qualifies for Personal Use?

- Individual users creating personal projects, portfolios, blogs, etc.
- Small non-profit organizations without significant revenue
- Educational projects and student work
- Open source community projects

### Key restrictions

- Cannot be used for commercial purposes or revenue-generating activities
- Cannot use the Organization JSON-LD schema on website homepage
- Cannot be used to promote or represent commercial entities

[Read the full Personal Use License →](/LICENSES/PERSONAL-USE.md)

